title: Advanced SystemCare Pro 9.0.3.1077 + serial patch

Advanced SystemCare Professional is a handy piece of software suite that contains essential components for increasing computer performance, protecting private information and blocking adware.


The user interface is very atrtractive and simple to follow. When you initate the software, you will be able to immediately select the skin and prefered language.


The "Quick Care" module is able to clean, repair and optimize the computer. The "Deep Care" option performs a complete scan on your computer for malware removal, deep registry fixing, registry defragmentation, system and startup optimization, shortcut repairing, privacy sweeping as well as cleaning junk files, not the mention security defence, disk scan, vulnerabillity fix and disk defrag.

The "Toolbox" offers solutions for cleaning (uninstaller, disk cleaner, file shredder), optimizing (Smart RAM, startup manager, Smart Defrag, game booster), repairing (undelete, shortcut fixer, disk doctor, Win Fix, IE Helper), security (system explorer, security holes scanner, process manager, driver manager, malware detector which needs to be seperarately installed) and controll (auto shutdown, disk explorer, system information, empty folder scanner, system controll).


Finally, the "Turbo Boost" module helps you optimize and speed up ther computer by following some simple steps - select boost mode (work or game mode), as well as disable unnecessary system services, non-Windows services, unnecessary background appl;ications and the Window theme.


Additionally, the "Rescue Center" will allow you to create a system restore point of your Windows and turn everything back to the Windows defaults.
All in all, Advanced SystemCare Professional works very well, and it uses minimum memory resources. It definitely has powerful features you need to maintain and protect your system.
